ox-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;联系电话：0871-68681294&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-margin-before:0em;-webkit-margin-after:0em;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;移动电话：13888384509 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 15198862744&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-margin-before:0em;-webkit-margin-after:0em;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-margin-before:0em;-webkit-margin-after:0em;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;1.地板太多头发？拿塑料袋套住扫把头发乖乖跟你走。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　2.浴室镜子上的水雾干湿毛巾都很难清理。可先在镜子上涂一层香皂，再用干抹布抹干，镜子很容易恢复清晰。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　3.冬天因干燥感到浑身发痒的，切不可用手抓，否则易抓破皮肤引起继发感染，可多饮水，多吃水果防治。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　4.喝咖啡可以缓解压力，放松心情，同时也可刺激肠蠕动。产生通便作用，为便秘所苦的人可以在早餐的时候喝咖啡。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　5.抽屉，壁橱衣箱里有霉味的时候，在里面放块肥皂，即可去除。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　6.买礼盒送人的时候，价格标签很难撕掉，可用吹风机吹热在撕，会很轻松的撕下来，不留一点痕迹。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　7.柚子皮煮水可治冻疮。用柚子皮煮水擦洗患处，每天洗1－2次，几次即可见效。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　8.牛奶可以强身健体，每天饮用250毫升牛奶可以降低患结肠癌的几率。但喝太多可能导致前列腺疾病。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　9.生姜能提神醒脑，冬季可适当多吃姜，专家认为吃生姜可舒解类风湿性关节炎所引起的疼痛，改善关节的活动能力。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　10.冬天忌将头蒙在被窝里，因为二氧化碳和不洁气体越积越多，会让人醒后感到昏昏沉沉，疲乏无力。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　11.绿豆退烧治感冒的窍门，可先煮绿豆，煮烂后在加姜丝和可乐，趁热喝下即可退烧治流感。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　12.喝牛奶前一小时不宜吃橘子，因为牛奶得蛋白质与橘子中得果酸相遇会发生凝固，不利于牛奶得吸收。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　13.香蕉皮能有效治冻伤，用香蕉皮得内面轻轻磨擦冻伤处，直至发热，几次即可见效。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　14.生吃花生米可治老花眼，每日吃花生米25克左右，每日一次，长期坚持对老花眼得恢复有帮助。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　15.橘皮水洗脸可润肤，用开水浸泡几片橘皮，待温度适宜后，用橘皮水洗脸,能润肤。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 16.钉钉子别用左手固定位置。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　17.游泳憋气能锻炼身体，对治疗耳鸣也有帮助，需长期坚持。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　18.茶叶中得儿茶素具有抑制流感病毒活性得作用，坚持用茶水漱口，可以有效预防流感。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　19.香蕉冰糖合蒸止咳，香蕉3根，冰糖5克,装入碗内上锅，文火蒸15分钟食用，止咳效果很好。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　20.花椒叶水泡脚治脚跟痛，将新鲜花椒叶水煮沸，趁热泡脚，连泡几天每次半小时，很快会痊愈。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　21.猪油蜂蜜膏能除冻疮，取猪油20克，蜂蜜80克，放在一起调匀成膏，敷于患处每日3次，数日克痊愈。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　22.姜汁饮料可治头晕恶心，用调味得姜粉配制饮料，乘车前半小时饮用，能防止头晕恶心。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　23.大枣治手脚裂，把数枚大枣去掉皮核，加水煮成糊状，涂抹于裂口处，一天两次，几天后可痊愈。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　24.酱油汗漱可治咽喉疼痛。咽喉疼痛时,用一调羹酱油漱口，1分钟左右吐出,连续3至4次,效果很好。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　25.若是木制家具裂了缝，可把旧报纸剪碎加明矾，米汤煮成糊状，将其嵌入裂缝，干燥后就很牢固了。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　26.将梨捣烂加冰糖调服，可治声音嘶哑，雪花梨加1克麻黄放入锅中煮熟，每天吃2次，可治百日咳。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　27.洗澡时身上若有伤口，可在伤口涂抹油质物，如面霜，与水隔离，就不会发炎，也不会痛了。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　28.报纸油墨可驱虫，在放衣服得箱子底下放一层报纸，在放入衣物，这样可使2衣物免遭虫咬。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　29.将适量鲜藕洗净，捣碎榨250克汁，加蜂蜜52克调匀，分5次服,连用数日,可治感冒咳嗽。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　30.巧克力不宜放在冰箱中,易发霉变质失去原味。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;31.易拉罐拉环套在大衣架上，把小衣架挂拉环上，省地。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　32.生食芦荟鲜叶早晚各6到9克，并用芦荟汁滴鼻，能治流感症状，服用4到5天即可。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　33.将花椒放入锅内炒糊,碾成面状，每晚睡前用适量白糖水冲服一汤匙花椒粉，常用可瘦身。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　34.慢性咽炎患者应多吃大白菜，勿食辛辣刺激食品，慢慢就可缓解这种病症。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　35.衣服上占了油垢后，稍挤牙膏涂于污染处，轻轻揉搓，然后用清水清洗，油渍即可除去。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　36.身体被磕碰后，即可用小磨香油涂抹患处，并轻轻揉一揉，患处便不会起肿块和出现青斑。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　37.白糖豆腐蒸食能治感冒，在豆腐上撒点白糖，用蒸锅熟后食用，一日3次，数日即可治愈感冒。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　38.用油炸食物，有时油烧沸后会从锅里溢出，可立即放进几粒花椒，沸油就好消下去。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　39.藤器弄脏了，可用水浸湿刷净，然后用点燃得硫黄熏，就会光洁如新。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　40.刚买回得陶瓷餐具，用4得食醋水浸泡煮沸，可去除大部分有毒物质。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　41.丝绸衣物烫黄时，可用少许苏打粉加水调成糊状，涂在焦迹处，待水蒸发后，在垫湿布熨烫，焦黄即可消除。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　42.在西红柿底部划个小十字，放入沸水中烫5秒钟，立即取出浸入冷水中，可轻易将皮剥掉。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　43.将150克枸杞放入适量白酒中浸泡,十几天后饮用,每日一次,长期饮用可有效治疗腰痛。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　44.每天晚饭后或临睡前,吃两瓣大蒜，一段时间后可治失眠，使睡眠恢复正常。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　45.艾草塞鼻可治鼻塞，将艾草揉好后塞入鼻中，会使鼻子呼吸通畅。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-margin-before:0em;-webkit-margin-after:0em;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;post_42997323&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;table id=&quot;pid42997323&quot; summary=&quot;pid42997323&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;empty-cells:show;table-layout:fixed;width:958px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tbody style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;tr style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;td class=&quot;plc&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 20px;word-wrap:break-word;vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;div class=&quot;pct&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 1em;&quot;&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;pcb&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;clear:left;&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;div class=&quot;t_fsz&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;min-height:100px;&quot;&gt;\r\n								&lt;table cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;empty-cells:show;table-layout:fixed;width:757px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;tbody style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;tr style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n											&lt;td class=&quot;t_f&quot; id=&quot;postmessage_42997323&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n												&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;font-size:large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;46.煮汤不溢锅。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　47.把蘸有甘油和蛋黄得布料盖在污渍表面放置片刻，用清水洗净即可去除污渍。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　48.开水服醋可防晕车，取少许醋,用开水饮用后然后乘车，可防晕车。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　49.专家建议冬天可多吃红辣椒，胡萝卜,山楂等食品，或每天喝一倍3酸奶,一碗鸡汤，都可有效预防感冒。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　50.冬季装修时，木材要注意保湿,以免变形，水工制品要及时封油，以防收缩，木地板要流出2毫米左右得伸缩缝。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　51.低温季节每天坚持搓耳，搓手，然后对这些部分用吹风机吹暖片刻，即可有效防治冻伤。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　52.秋冬季节,每日煮食白萝卜，胡萝卜，连汤带菜早晚各服一小碗，长期坚持，可有效治疗慢性支气管炎。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　53.毛衣穿久了，有些部位会磨得发亮，用醋，水各半得混合液喷撒一下，在洗涤.就好恢复原样。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　54.秋天眼中有红血丝，可吃杞菊地黄丸(河南宛西,兰州佛慈)。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　55.熬粥放入橘皮，不仅芳香可口，而且还能起到开胃作用，对于胸腹胀满或咳嗽痰多得人，有治疗作用。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　56.秋冬季节手脚干裂，可将剩茶水兑血热水泡洗手脚约10分钟,坚持一周，皮肤即可光滑如初。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　57.白色毛衣穿久会发黑，将毛衣清洗后放入冰箱冷冻一小时，取出在晾干,即可洁白如新。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　58.抽油烟机上得油盒很难清洗，可在干净得油盒上先放点水，让油滴在水上，快清洗时一倒，油很快久倒出来了。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　59.在皴裂得手脚上涂些牙膏,就能止血止痛，很快痊愈。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt; \r\n											&lt;/td&gt;\r\n										&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n									&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n								&lt;/table&gt;\r\n							&lt;/div&gt;\r\n							&lt;div id=&quot;comment_42997323&quot; class=&quot;cm&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;/div&gt;\r\n							&lt;div id=&quot;post_rate_div_42997323&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;/div&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;/div&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;tr style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;td class=&quot;plc plm&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 20px;word-wrap:break-word;vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;div class=&quot;sign&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:20px 0px 10px;overflow:hidden;line-height:1.6em;background-image:url(http://www.deyi.com/static/image/common/sigline.gif);max-height:40px;background-position:0px 0px;background-repeat:no-repeat no-repeat;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;/div&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n	&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;post_42997328&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;table id=&quot;pid42997328&quot; summary=&quot;pid42997328&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;empty-cells:show;table-layout:fixed;width:958px;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;tbody style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n			&lt;tr style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;td class=&quot;pls&quot; rowspan=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;width:160px;background-color:#E5EDF2;border-right-width:1px;border-right-style:solid;border-right-color:#C2D5E3;background-position:initial initial;background-repeat:initial initial;&quot;&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n				&lt;td class=&quot;plc&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 20px;word-wrap:break-word;vertical-align:top;overflow:hidden;&quot;&gt;\r\n					&lt;div class=&quot;pct&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 1em;&quot;&gt;\r\n						&lt;div class=&quot;pcb&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;clear:left;&quot;&gt;\r\n							&lt;div class=&quot;t_fsz&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;min-height:100px;&quot;&gt;\r\n								&lt;table cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;empty-cells:show;table-layout:fixed;width:757px;&quot;&gt;\r\n									&lt;tbody style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n										&lt;tr style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot;&gt;\r\n											&lt;td class=&quot;t_f&quot; id=&quot;postmessage_42997328&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n												&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;font-size:large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 60.看电视发现遥控器找不到了，在沙发里里外外翻来翻去很是头疼脑热？用尼龙粘扣把遥控器放在茶几边上，用的时候找得到。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　61.棉质衣服出现霉斑，用几根绿豆牙在霉斑得地方反复揉搓，然后用清水漂洗干净，霉斑即可去除。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　62.冬天吃萝卜得妙处：可解毒，治小便不利等症状。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　63.冬天忌睡前洗头，冷天用热水洗完头之后，大量水分蒸发时带走很多热量，这时候睡觉,易患感冒。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　64.花生米可治风寒胃疼,受冷风刺激之后常会引起胃疼，可吃些煮熟炒熟的花生米，胃疼即可减轻。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　65.将鸡蛋磕破，分离蛋黄和蛋白，将蛋黄到入鲜牛奶中同煮，饮后可起到镇脑安神的功效。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　66.碘酒外抹患处能除手藓，在患处每天抹碘酒4到5次，患处皮肤逐渐干而脱落，手藓随之治愈。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　67.在玻璃伤先涂点石膏粉和粉笔灰水，干后再用干布擦可轻易将玻璃擦亮。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　68.啤酒漱口可去尘消霉，用啤酒漱口可以冲掉喉咙里的微尘，并有消毒的作用,可以使喉咙更舒畅。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　69.白酒治汗脚臭脚.每晚洗脚后用白酒少许揉搓脚部,并自然风干，坚持一个月，可治愈脚臭。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　70.巧刷翻毛皮鞋，用酒精和黄米面调成糊状涂于鞋面.晾干后把黄米面刷掉，脏东西就会随之除掉。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　71.多吃水煮鱼易产生皮肤问题，水煮鱼中的辣椒刺激性强，一些餐馆用海鱼做源料，部分食客会有过敏反应。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　72.巧洗羊毛衫：洗涤时放在温水中加适量干洗剂和氨水，漂洗时在加几滴醋,可帮助恢复毛织物原有的光泽及柔软度。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　73.豆腐放冰箱中保鲜的窍门，豆腐直接放入冰箱，水分会溢出，风味也差，可泡在水中存放冰箱内。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　74.煮可乐可治伤风感冒。伤风感冒初起时，可用可乐加几片姜和一个柠檬同煮，然后饮之,既有显著疗效。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n											&lt;/td&gt;\r\n										&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n									&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n								&lt;/table&gt;\r\n							&lt;/div&gt;\r\n						&lt;/div&gt;\r\n					&lt;/div&gt;\r\n				&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n	&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:large;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 90.莲蓬头有的眼堵了？用塑料袋里倒点醋像这样扎在喷头上泡一夜，通了。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;color:#444444;font-family:Tahoma, Helvetica, SimSun, sans-serif, Hei;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:24px;&quot;&gt;　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　91.脚枕枕头治抽筋，每晚睡觉时在脚下垫一个枕头，可防治抽筋症状在睡觉时发生。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　92.涂抹肥皂可消肿止痛，不论是被开水或火烫伤后，立刻在伤处涂抹些肥皂，可暂时消肿止痛。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　93.海带泥掺蜂蜜治口疮，将海带(或茄子皮)烤焦倒碎,掺入蜂蜜后涂抹在患处,效果很好。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　94.空腹吃核桃仁可治风湿，每天空腹吃5-6个核桃，坚持几个月后，风湿症状可消失。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　95.如果毛衣袖口或下摆失去了弹性，可在热水中浸泡20分钟，通风干燥处晾干后即可恢复弹性。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　96.要清除冰箱霉菌，可用干布蘸肥皂水擦拭，如擦不掉，可用干布蘸上少量酒精擦拭。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　97.按摩眼眶治鼻炎，双手食指按在两眼下的眼眶骨，每天两次揉二百下，一段时间后可见效。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　98.嚼吃花生有效治倒牙，嚼几粒花生或一段生葱，牙齿立即恢复如初,就可以继续嚼东西了。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　99.牛奶能使鱼汤鲜美，在家炖鱼汤时可在锅里滴几滴牛奶，这样不仅可使鱼肉白嫩,鱼汤也会很美味。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　100.用完的香水瓶，化妆水瓶不要立即扔掉，把他们的盖打开，放在衣箱或衣柜里会使衣物变得香气袭人。&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　&lt;br style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;&quot; /&gt;\r\n　　101.旧丝袜套在吸尘器吸嘴上找零碎东西。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-high