);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;移动电话：13888384509 &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; 15198862744&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-margin-before:0em;-webkit-margin-after:0em;color:#444444;font-family:arial, 微软雅黑;font-size:14px;line-height:20px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.5;font-size:32px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing:border-box;font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;北京某高干子弟和山西煤老板儿子吃饭，高干子弟大声道：“给老子一百万，在北京 没有我办不到的事”。煤老板儿子听后小声说：“哥，我给你一个亿，能不能把天安门城楼上那张照片换成我爹的？”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;1&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/hOkKMC2fTLt*7L1UihwedJTmoWVjBbHPLEL29MbB2qM!/b/YT1v.poaGgAAYoQW*5oPGgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/hOkKMC2fTLt*7L1UihwedJTmoWVjBbHPLEL29MbB2qM!/b/YT1v.poaGgAAYoQW*5oPGgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n和同事等公交，旁边站一喝豆浆漂亮MM。同事开玩笑说：哥，你的车呢？我说：送去修了；MM往我身边靠了点，同事顺势继续说：咋回事？我接着编：和个大奔追尾了。同事继续装：哎呀，那得多少钱！要不我给你去找找朋友；我说：不用，一个脚蹬子能值几个钱！然后MM的豆浆喷了一地...&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;2&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b221.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/HWRLAbj48wsTm58xhHGz21XfjQMXhAgVDssle4c*s8c!/b/YUsjw4MwAwAAYjA9yYNGAwAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b221.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/HWRLAbj48wsTm58xhHGz21XfjQMXhAgVDssle4c*s8c!/b/YUsjw4MwAwAAYjA9yYNGAwAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n中国特色的脑筋急转弯：１问：边做假药广告边痛斥假药危害的是什么？答：江湖骗 子。错，是ＣＣＴＶ。２问：比上大学还贵的是什么？答：出国留学。错，是幼儿园 。３问：为什么有人从几千米高直接跌落到不足千米却面不改色心不跳？答：是在跳 伞。错，是中国股民；４问：明明口袋里只有３０元，却搞一大堆数据证明实际有１ ００元的是什么人？答：骗子。错，是统计局。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;3&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b214.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/eGShyxMtdALSMJE4D1zwNlBqpG2m70J3mMfL6d9XMeQ!/b/YSPdkH.ZmAAAYs31k3.CmAAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b214.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/eGShyxMtdALSMJE4D1zwNlBqpG2m70J3mMfL6d9XMeQ!/b/YSPdkH.ZmAAAYs31k3.CmAAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n几十个高官们坐飞机去旅游，其中一个省长说：我丢个100元纸币下去，谁捡到了谁准高兴。一个市长说：不如丢十张十元下去，10个人都会高兴。另一个区长说：干脆丢100个一元硬币下去，一百个人捡到一百个人高兴。飞行员沉不住气了：不如我把你们全丢下去，让全国人民都高兴高兴？&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;4&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b214.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/ItnDs6aumnWU73gQQxkJzD7Hq*zvXNDJr2.FEuw7Y7I!/b/YYFqkn*smwAAYqJvkn8UmgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b214.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/ItnDs6aumnWU73gQQxkJzD7Hq*zvXNDJr2.FEuw7Y7I!/b/YYFqkn*smwAAYqJvkn8UmgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n天堂门坏了，上帝要招标重修。 印度人说：3千元就弄好，理由是材料费1千，人工费1千，我自己赚1千。 来个德国人说：要6千元，材料费2千，人工2千，自己赚2千。 最后中国人淡定地说：这个要9千元，3千给你，3千我的，剩下3千 给那个印度人干。 上帝拍案称奇，好就给你做！&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;5&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b213.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/CY8OV9HruMUlxw0o6xm6a0x9YSvUj87a4ywnVTy6Zls!/b/YS9T.37rmgAAYtx7BH8LmgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b213.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/CY8OV9HruMUlxw0o6xm6a0x9YSvUj87a4ywnVTy6Zls!/b/YS9T.37rmgAAYtx7BH8LmgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n广东一伙劫匪在抢劫银行时说了一句至理名言：&quot;通通不许动，钱是国家的，命是自己的！大家都一声不吭躺倒。劫匪望了一眼躺在桌上四肢朝天的出纳小姐，说：&quot;请你躺文明些！这是抢劫，又不是强奸！劫匪回去后，其中一个新来的硕士劫匪说，老大，我们赶快数一下抢了多少，那老劫匪（小学文化）说，你傻啊？这么多，你要数到什么时候啊？今天晚上看新闻不就知道了吗。这就叫工作经验，这年头工作经验比学历更重要。 劫匪走后，行长说，赶紧报案！主任刚要走，行长急忙说：“等等！把我们上次私自挪用的那五百万也加上去！”主任说：“要是劫匪每个月都来抢一回就好了”。----这就叫工作经验，这年头工作经验比学历更重要结果，第二天新闻联播报道银行被抢了一亿，劫匪数来数去只有两千万。老大骂道：“妈的，老子拼了一条命才抢了两千万，银行行长动动手指头就赚了八千万，看来这年头还是要读书啊！&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;6&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b217.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/ub.5o4IPvTXFFccX23qNkN9DyADcXKzxYZGJ5OrIJ6Y!/b/YcJUZYE*dAAAYu1OZYEkdQAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b217.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/ub.5o4IPvTXFFccX23qNkN9DyADcXKzxYZGJ5OrIJ6Y!/b/YcJUZYE*dAAAYu1OZYEkdQAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n一美国人到中国旅游，用20万美元换134万人民币，100万买一单身公寓，34万吃喝玩乐一年。第二年要回去了，房子涨了卖了200万，人民币兑美元升值到1:5，200万人民币换回40万美元。美国人在中国白玩一年还倒挣20万美元，高高兴兴地回家了！ 统计局也很高兴，因为GDP增长了！&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;7&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b214.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/A3ef9CNCySi.3.ZRel.urQsuT*sRTUh5QM.ch1FA2SY!/b/YccYnX83mAAAYn2woX8KmwAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b214.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/A3ef9CNCySi.3.ZRel.urQsuT*sRTUh5QM.ch1FA2SY!/b/YccYnX83mAAAYn2woX8KmwAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n王老师外出度假，临走前担心家中被盗，便在客厅桌上放了一百块钱并给小偷留纸条：您别费神了，我们家我都找不到钱，这一百块钱给您零花。隔壁家是铁道部的，有钱而且还不敢报案。等度假回来，王老板发现桌子上钱变成了二十万！在他留给小偷的纸条的反面写着：给您的信息费，请笑纳!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;8&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b218.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/Xe.Xxc6twl3vb5JdH1dAQL3daOiRJ.A4QIngWXy7LC4!/b/YUqQBYL3KgAAYk9k*IH8KgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b218.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/Xe.Xxc6twl3vb5JdH1dAQL3daOiRJ.A4QIngWXy7LC4!/b/YUqQBYL3KgAAYk9k*IH8KgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n某省长因贪腐入狱，儿子大学毕业，找不着工作，探监时诉苦。爸爸写了一字条儿，让儿子找他以前的下属帮忙。儿子问：人走茶凉，现在写条子，有用吗？爸爸说：我在台上的时候，想让谁当官，就让谁当，现在，我在监狱里，想让谁进来，谁就得进来，放心吧，儿子，我的条子还是照样有效！”&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;9&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b222.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/ovmFpEtLoC.xWyF6NJpvKkyUD3jVjVhH.DLX.VCSA1g!/b/YRw*YISPAAAAYpwyXYTuAAAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b222.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/ovmFpEtLoC.xWyF6NJpvKkyUD3jVjVhH.DLX.VCSA1g!/b/YRw*YISPAAAAYpwyXYTuAAAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n一干部酒后和小姐潇洒被查，领导要求他写下过程并作深刻检讨，这干部一句话高度概括为“巴掌大的地方犯下天大的错误!”领导看后觉得很深刻，但嫌过于抽象，要求细化。于是这干部又写下十点：1、一人寂寞；2、两个人快活；3、三分钟快感；4、四百元小费；5、五千元罚款；6、六个月工资没了；7、七天拘留亏大了；8、倒了八辈子血霉；9、都是酒惹的祸；10、我十分后悔!&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;10&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/UHEuud2ytzuZax1rFUVGEx4Izzmo61vXjXWuZQg9Pjk!/b/YQqbA5vwGQAAYpkL*Jr4GQAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/UHEuud2ytzuZax1rFUVGEx4Izzmo61vXjXWuZQg9Pjk!/b/YQqbA5vwGQAAYpkL*Jr4GQAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n一位小姐独自走在黑暗的地下通道里，突然，一个男子张着双臂向她走来！小姐见状，临危不乱!为了保护自己，她飞起一脚踢向那人要害!只听“哗啦”一声！那男子委屈的长啸到：“妈的，这已是让人踹碎的第三块玻璃了”。&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;11&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/O4Id96T7z.eYt5dvd.iX2IisiKV1iyB2IOX8ZHCeUB4!/b/YfmzBpv8GQAAYj6LA5szGgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/O4Id96T7z.eYt5dvd.iX2IisiKV1iyB2IOX8ZHCeUB4!/b/YfmzBpv8GQAAYj6LA5szGgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n我是临时工，他是领导。我月薪2千，他月入20万，我们人均收入10.1万；我的宿舍10平，他的别墅290平，我们人均住房150平我一餐8元，他一餐8万，我们人均每餐消费4万；我有80元的单车，他有80万的奥迪，我们人均40万的座驾；我是光棍，他有1个老婆9个二奶，我们人均5个女人谁还敢说国人不幸福?&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;12&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/kTdybWOaW94QkhAqw5FypililgCmJ5uJEG6PGfrTC5g!/b/YRcPApssGgAAYscaBZsWGgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b260.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/kTdybWOaW94QkhAqw5FypililgCmJ5uJEG6PGfrTC5g!/b/YRcPApssGgAAYscaBZsWGgAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n深夜，一个醉汉摇摇晃晃的进了一家旅店，他来到吧台对服务员说：“给我拿225房间的钥匙。”服务员说：“先生，225房间有人住了。”醉汉生气地说：“有人住？那我住哪？”服务员说：“您是不是找错旅店了？”醉汉大声地说：“错不了，我记得你们旅店门口有标志。”“啥标志？”“顾客您好，欢迎光临。”&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-img-idx=&quot;13&quot; data-src=&quot;http://b217.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/CNMuL7k.W9K*WiT1PV1ahNcFtnQeVXvJFpZ3MmwEVOs!/b/YeOpWoFhdQAAYn.tXYEbcwAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; src=&quot;http://b217.photo.store.qq.com/psb?/f55005bb-2d9b-40bf-8135-23fa8395baa7/CNMuL7k.W9K*WiT1PV1ahNcFtnQeVXvJFpZ3MmwEVOs!/b/YeOpWoFhdQAAYn.tXYEbcwAA&amp;amp;ek=1&amp;amp;kp=1&amp;amp;pt=0&amp;amp;t=5&amp;amp;sce=0-12-12&amp;amp;rf=2-9&quot; style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;border-style:none;vertical-align:top;&quot; /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n一个酒鬼喝醉后上厕所方便，很快就回来了，兴奋地说：“这里的生意太好了，连厕所都摆了两桌！”这时，一个客人领着一个保安过来了，指着酒鬼说：“就是他，刚才在我们包间里撒尿！”&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:punctuation, 微软雅黑, Tohoma;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;white-space:normal;background-color:#000000;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/div&gt;\r\n	&lt;div style=&quot;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-famil